content: Yes, the Dell Inspiron 14 5000 also comes with a touchscreen display. It has a 14-inch FHD IPS LED-Backlit touchscreen display that supports resolutions of up to 1920 x 1080 pixels. This can be helpful for navigating through applications or scrolling through documents, as you mentioned. It also comes with a stylus that can be used for drawing or taking notes on the touchscreen display.
